&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Motus is the industry leader in vehicle reimbursement and risk mitigation solutions for employees who drive. Combining 80 years of&amp;nbsp;expertise&amp;nbsp;with innovative technology, Motus enables organizations to&amp;nbsp;optimize&amp;nbsp;spend&amp;nbsp;and increase productivity across their workforce. With solutions purpose-built to enable data-driven insights and strategic decision making, Motus is the preferred vehicle reimbursement partner to top Fortune 500 companies globally. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:120}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
