&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Motus is seeking a Senior Demand Generation Manager to lead integrated campaign strategy and execution in support of pipeline growth. Reporting to the VP of Demand, this role is responsible for the planning, orchestration, and performance of campaigns built to generate pipeline for the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role focuses on translating key moments (pillar content, events, product launched) into cohesive, cross-channel campaigns that align Marketing, BDR, Sales Enablement, Partner, Customer, and Sales teams around shared pipeline goals. The Senior Manager, Demand Generation will serve as the connective tissue between teams ensuring campaigns are tightly integrated, well-timed, and optimized to drive measurable business impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate possesses a solid operational backbone and is a strategic campaign leader. They deeply understand B2B buyer journeys and enjoy building repeatable, scalable demand engines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Duties: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end strategy, execution, and optimization of integrated demand generation campaigns focused on generating pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage a campaign framework centered on key pillar moments, aligning messaging, channels, and timing across the full marketing mix, segments, and new and existing business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with BDR, Sales Enablement, and Sales to align campaigns to target accounts, territories, and pipeline goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate company priorities, ICPs, and buyer insights into compelling campaign themes, offers, and activation plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orchestrate cross-functional execution with Sales Enablement, Digital, Brand, Customer, Events, Product Marketing, Marketing Operations, and Campaign Operations to deliver cohesive, multi-channel campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure campaigns are tightly aligned to buyer journeys and funnel stages, from awareness through sales engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own campaign performance measurement, working with BDR and Revenue Operations to track impact on new business pipeline, conversion, and velocity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze results and continuously optimize campaign strategy, messaging, and channel mix based on performance insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage campaign calendars, prioritization, and resource allocation to maximize impact and focus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a partner to stakeholders, clearly communicating plans, results, and recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on demand generation best practices, competitive landscape, and emerging approaches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
